Beutner Says Stadium Plan Costs L.A. `Not a Nickel'

-- B y  
-- 
2011-03-14T22:43:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-14/beutner-says-stadium-plan-costs-l-a-not-a-nickel-video.html
  Los Angeles  First Deputy Mayor 
Austin Beutner  talks with Bloomberg's Matt Winkler, Christopher
Palmeri and Daniel Taub about billionaire Philip Anschutz's 
proposal to build a professional football stadium in downtown 
Los Angeles.  Beutner says Anschutz Entertainment Group's backing of Los 
Angeles city bonds insures public funds aren't risked on the 
$1.35 billion stadium plan. They spoke on March 9. (Source: 
Bloomberg)  Running time 10:52  -0- Mar/14/2011 22:43 GMT
 